msg: Updated to reflect new Application interface. Application no longer implements Container and operates independently of it.

author: donaldp
msg: Refactored DefaultEmbeddor to be less verbose and to construct/setup all components using standard methods rather than custom methods. This ended up with less complexity overall in Embeddor.

author: donaldp
msg: Interface no longer implements Startable (not needed) but does implement Executable (which wasn't around when Embeddor interface was originally constructed).

author: donaldp
msg: Embeddor no longer implements Startable and thus no longer call start/stop()
